  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SuperSpec Rallycross is a top-down racer for Rallycross fans. It's a quick and casual blast of nostalgia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Retro fueled, just like you remember</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by our favorites growing up from the 80's and 90's, SuperSpec Rallycross drives just like you'd expect if you found it in the arcade.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/8601b0f69b433a1741566fc8cf501918.poster.avif?t=1734837877\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/8601b0f69b433a1741566fc8cf501918.webm?t=1734837877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/8601b0f69b433a1741566fc8cf501918.mp4?t=1734837877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Less serious, more fun</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SuperSpec Rallycross is easy for new drivers and satisfying for enthusiasts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/1d9d48f1dfb6ace8bd3737058f684c35.poster.avif?t=1734837877\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/1d9d48f1dfb6ace8bd3737058f684c35.webm?t=1734837877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/1d9d48f1dfb6ace8bd3737058f684c35.mp4?t=1734837877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Joker lap strategy</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A joker lap is an alternate route each driver must take once during a race. Taking the joker at the perfect time and place is part of the race strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/32f25317b8785b322702daff905d722a.poster.avif?t=1734837877\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/32f25317b8785b322702daff905d722a.webm?t=1734837877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/32f25317b8785b322702daff905d722a.mp4?t=1734837877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Split-screen party play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple controls, a familiar game loop, and a charming style make SuperSpec Rallycross the perfect party game. It supports up to four players in local split-screen!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/4299f7549357ed6e60469fbf926e3f66.poster.avif?t=1734837877\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/4299f7549357ed6e60469fbf926e3f66.webm?t=1734837877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/4299f7549357ed6e60469fbf926e3f66.mp4?t=1734837877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the Developer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SuperSpec Rallycross is the passion project of a solo developer inspired by classic arcade racing games. Thank you for supporting indie development—your feedback is invaluable in shaping the future of the SuperSpec series! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/ce6e3d6b0d716759144abbc9d955044f.poster.avif?t=1734837877\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/ce6e3d6b0d716759144abbc9d955044f.webm?t=1734837877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/ce6e3d6b0d716759144abbc9d955044f.mp4?t=1734837877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Grand Prix</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A four-race series where points are awarded for race position, fast laps, and joker laps taken. The points leader takes all!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Single Race</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A quick race with the classic Rallycross ruleset.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Time Trial</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A ghost race to compete against your fastest lap times and challenge friends for online leaderboard dominance!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Split-Screen Multiplayer</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A local multiplayer experience with both Single Race and Grand Prix modes available. (Supports online play via Steam Remote Play Together.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlockable Content</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 Unique circuits inspired by the sport's most beloved real-world locations. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12 Rallycross cars - 6 modern marvels - 6 rally icons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 Achievements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random (4 Race) Cup Generator.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Full Gamepad Support</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gamepads are fully featured and are the recommended way to play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Full Steam Deck Support</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Verified to play great on Steam Deck.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SuperSpec Rallycross is a top-down racer for Rallycross fans. It's a quick and casual blast of nostalgia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Retro fueled, just like you remember</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by our favorites growing up from the 80's and 90's, SuperSpec Rallycross drives just like you'd expect if you found it in the arcade.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/8601b0f69b433a1741566fc8cf501918.poster.avif?t=1734837877\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/8601b0f69b433a1741566fc8cf501918.webm?t=1734837877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/8601b0f69b433a1741566fc8cf501918.mp4?t=1734837877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Less serious, more fun</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SuperSpec Rallycross is easy for new drivers and satisfying for enthusiasts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/1d9d48f1dfb6ace8bd3737058f684c35.poster.avif?t=1734837877\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/1d9d48f1dfb6ace8bd3737058f684c35.webm?t=1734837877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/1d9d48f1dfb6ace8bd3737058f684c35.mp4?t=1734837877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Joker lap strategy</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A joker lap is an alternate route each driver must take once during a race. Taking the joker at the perfect time and place is part of the race strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/32f25317b8785b322702daff905d722a.poster.avif?t=1734837877\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/32f25317b8785b322702daff905d722a.webm?t=1734837877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/32f25317b8785b322702daff905d722a.mp4?t=1734837877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Split-screen party play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple controls, a familiar game loop, and a charming style make SuperSpec Rallycross the perfect party game. It supports up to four players in local split-screen!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/4299f7549357ed6e60469fbf926e3f66.poster.avif?t=1734837877\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/4299f7549357ed6e60469fbf926e3f66.webm?t=1734837877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/4299f7549357ed6e60469fbf926e3f66.mp4?t=1734837877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the Developer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SuperSpec Rallycross is the passion project of a solo developer inspired by classic arcade racing games. Thank you for supporting indie development—your feedback is invaluable in shaping the future of the SuperSpec series! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/ce6e3d6b0d716759144abbc9d955044f.poster.avif?t=1734837877\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/ce6e3d6b0d716759144abbc9d955044f.webm?t=1734837877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/ce6e3d6b0d716759144abbc9d955044f.mp4?t=1734837877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Grand Prix</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A four-race series where points are awarded for race position, fast laps, and joker laps taken. The points leader takes all!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Single Race</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A quick race with the classic Rallycross ruleset.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Time Trial</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A ghost race to compete against your fastest lap times and challenge friends for online leaderboard dominance!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Split-Screen Multiplayer</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A local multiplayer experience with both Single Race and Grand Prix modes available. (Supports online play via Steam Remote Play Together.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlockable Content</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 Unique circuits inspired by the sport's most beloved real-world locations. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12 Rallycross cars - 6 modern marvels - 6 rally icons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 Achievements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random (4 Race) Cup Generator.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Full Gamepad Support</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gamepads are fully featured and are the recommended way to play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Full Steam Deck Support</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Verified to play great on Steam Deck.</p>",
